                    <msContents>
                        <summary>The first volume of a five-volume set containing stories from the
                            Arabian Nights and other sources. This volume contains dialogues,
                            grammar, anthology, and proverbs. It is divided into four maqalahs and
                            subdivided into fasls.</summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="manuscript_13838-item1">
                            <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_700">Alf laylah
                                wa-laylah</title>
                            <title xml:lang="ar">الف ليلة وليلة؛ فى حروف العربية ووضعهم بالكلام؛ فى
                                ضرب الكلام بالمخاطبة لتعليم اللغة العربية؛ فى بعض حكايات ضحكية
                                لتعليم امتداد القول العربى</title>
                            <title xml:lang="en" type="supplied">A Thousand and One Nights</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                            <note><p>This volume contains dialogues, grammar, anthology, and
                                    proverbs. It is divided into four maḳālahs and subdivided into
                                    faṣls.</p><p>For the other volumes of the set, see <ref
                                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_13834"
                                        >Arabic MS 134</ref> (Vol. 1), <ref
                                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_13835"
                                        >Arabic MS 135</ref> (Vol. 2), <ref
                                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_13836"
                                        >Arabic MS 136</ref> (Vol. 3), <ref
                                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_13837"
                                        >Arabic MS 137</ref> (Vol. 4).</p></note>
                            <msItem xml:id="Arabic_MS_138-item1-item1">
                                <locus from="1b" to="">1b-</locus>
                                <title xml:lang="en">First maḳālah</title>
                                <note><p>The first maḳālah has seven faṣls: <quote xml:lang="ar">في
                                            حروف العربية ووضعهم بالكلام</quote>.</p></note>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="Arabic_MS_138-item1-item2">
                                <locus from="2b" to="">2b-</locus>
                                <title xml:lang="en">Second maḳālah</title>
                                <note><p>It has seven faṣls: <quote xml:lang="ar">في ضرب الكلام
                                            بالمخاطبة لتعليم اللغة العربة</quote>.</p></note>
                            </msItem>

                            <msItem xml:id="Arabic_MS_138-item1-item3">
                                <locus from="2b" to="">2b-</locus>
                                <title xml:lang="en">Third maḳālah containing stories</title>
                                <note><p><quote xml:lang="ar">في بعض حكايات ضحكية لتعليم اهتداد
                                            القول العربي</quote>.</p>
                                </note>
